	body
		.overlay
			.header
				#brand
					img#logo(src='img/norstar-white.svg')
				.carousel
					.carousel-fixed
						#slogan 
							h1 What Recycling 
							h1 Should Look Like
						h1.carousel-header Recycling Should
					.carousel-moving
						h1#carousel1 Skip the Landfill
						h1#carousel2 Cost Less
						h1#carousel3 Be About the Future
						h1#carousel4 Be Your Best Option
			a.page-up
				img.down-button(src='img/arrow-up.svg')
			.action-button_floating
			a.page-down
				img.down-button(src='img/arrow-down.svg')
			.footer
				a(href="http://www.jordanlos.com"): p.footer-p Design By Jordan
				a(href="http://www.freepik.com"): p.footer-p Icons by Freepik
		#content
			.content#section1
				img.icon(src='img/recycle.svg')
				p By recycling impacted soils, we can avoid costly intermediate solutions like landfills. Our commitment to resourcefulness means we find new environmentally friendly uses for contaminated soils instead of just moving the liability elsewhere.
			.content#section2
				img.icon(src='img/money.svg')
				p Businesses shouldn't have to choose between doing the right thing for the environment and saving money. We are committed to offering significant savings on remediation costs. When we can accomplish the same goals with less resources both businesses and the environment benefit .
			.content#section3
				img.icon(src='img/kids.svg')
				p Why pass the liability to the next generation? Our commitment to sustainability means we don't just move contaminants, we elimiate them. We think our children shouldn't have to deal with our contaminants, just in a different location.
			.content#section4
				img.icon(src='img/call.svg')
				p Want to learn more about Norstar Environmental or curious about recycling other materials?
